Package: sora
Title: Shared Objects for R Applications
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Charlie", "Gao", , "charlie.gao@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0750-061X")),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"),
           comment = c(ROR = "03wc8by49"))
  )
Description: Share R objects across processes on the same machine without
    copying. Uses 'POSIX' shared memory on Linux and macOS, and 'Win32'
    file mappings on Windows, so that multiple R processes can read the
    same physical memory pages. Integrates with the R 'ALTREP' framework for
    lazy, zero-copy access, with shared objects serialized compactly by
    their shared memory name rather than their full contents.
